display="inline"><![CDATA[(x\star 0)+(x\star 0)=x\star 0]]></fr:tex> and then subtracting <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\star 0]]></fr:tex> from both sides gives us <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\star 0=0]]></fr:tex> as desired.</fr:p><html:span
